  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI-driven shipment management with formula templates and dynamic freight rating",
    "Full fleet management for tractors, trailers, and equipment types",
    "Worker management including profiles, PTO, and compliance tracking",
    "Real-time dispatch and assignment engine powered by Temporal workflows",
    "Hazardous materials compliance with DOT reference data and segregation rules",
    "Customer management with billing controls and accessorial charge support",
    "Fiscal year and GL account management for integrated financial reporting",
    "Role-based access control with fine-grained resource permissions",
    "External integrations: Google Maps, Samsara, OpenAI, and HERE routing",
    "Full-text search via Meilisearch with real-time change data capture (CDC)",
    "Table change alerts and audit logging for operational visibility",
    "Self-hosted Docker deployment with Caddy reverse proxy and TLS automation"
  ],
